Class Reservation

java.lang.Object
com.iunera.jsonldjava.schemaorg.metadatatypes.Thing
com.iunera.jsonldjava.schemaorg.metadatatypes.Intangible
com.iunera.jsonldjava.schemaorg.metadatatypes.Reservation
Direct Known Subclasses:
BusReservation, EventReservation, FlightReservation, FoodEstablishmentReservation, LodgingReservation, RentalCarReservation, ReservationPackage, TaxiReservation, TrainReservation
public class Reservation extends Intangible
Describes a reservation for travel, dining or an event. Some reservations require tickets. Note: This type is for information about actual reservations, e.g. in confirmation emails or HTML pages with individual confirmations of reservations. For offers of tickets, restaurant reservations, flights, or rental cars, use Offer.
